descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 20 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
Play the world’s second most popular sport with 2+ billion fans now in an epic VR cricket experience. Final Overs takes cricket gaming to the next level in VR with innovative physics, aesthetic world-class stadiums, & many more exciting gameplay features.

Step into the jam-packed virtual stadiums & establish your cricketing legacy as an aspiring cricketer. Take on AI-powered bowling side, or compete with your friends in local multiplayer matches. 

[media]

World-class matches in **aesthetic stadiums**

[media]

Fully immersive experience with **realistic physics**

[media]

Thrilling matches against **international teams**

[media]

Polish your batting skills with **timing meter**

[media]

Challenge friends in **local multiplayer** mode using mobile

[media]

**OTHER FEATURES:**

- Multiple cricket formats: quick match, T20, ODI
- Track your progress in your profile
- AI-driven intelligent fielding & bowling system
- AI Coach match summary & tips
- Multiple difficulty levels
- Immersive world-class stadiums
- Practice net
- Regular updates

These, and many other incoming features make Final Overs worth the experience. DOWNLOAD now and rise as a star in VR cricket!
